#: src/views/search_autocomplete.py:1674
msgid ""
"<b>Advanced Search Syntax:</b><br><br>• <code>domain:example.com</code> -"
" Filter by domain<br>• <code>after:2023-01-01</code> - Visit after "
"date<br>• <code>before:2023-12-31</code> - Visit before date<br>• "
"<code>-keyword</code> - Exclude term<br>• <code>title:keyword</code> - "
"Search only titles<br>• <code>url:keyword</code> - Search only URLs<br>• "
"<code>browser:chrome</code> - Filter by browser type<br>• "
"<code>device:laptop</code> - Filter by device name<br><br><b>Bookmark "
"Filters:</b><br>• <code>is:bookmarked</code> - Only bookmarked "
"records<br>• <code>has:note</code> - Only records with annotations<br>• "
"<code>tag:work</code> - Filter by bookmark tag<br><br><i>Tip: You can "
"combine these tokens with regular text.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<b>고급 검색 문법:</b><br><br>• <code>domain:example.com</code> - 도메인별 필터<br>• "
"<code>after:2023-01-01</code> - 해당 날짜 이후 방문<br>• "
"<code>before:2023-12-31</code> - 해당 날짜 이전 방문<br>• <code>-keyword</code> -"
" 해당 단어 제외<br>• <code>title:keyword</code> - 제목만 검색<br>• "
"<code>url:keyword</code> - URL만 검색<br>• <code>browser:chrome</code> - "
"브라우저 종류별 필터<br>• <code>device:laptop</code> - 기기 이름별 필터<br><br><b>북마크 "
"필터:</b><br>• <code>is:bookmarked</code> - 북마크된 레코드만<br>• "
"<code>has:note</code> - 메모가 있는 레코드만<br>• <code>tag:work</code> - 북마크 태그별 "
"필터<br><br><i>팁: 일반 텍스트와 이러한 토큰을 함께 사용할 수 있습니다.</i>"

